<item>
            <title>[PIG-2871] Refactor signature for PigReducerEstimator</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2871</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The signature to this method should be refactored to provide more context so the implementer has access to the map and reduce plans. Also passing both &lt;tt&gt;Job&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;Configuration&lt;/tt&gt; is redundant, since the latter can be obtained by the former.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose changing this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;int estimateNumberOfReducers(Configuration conf, List&amp;lt;POLoad&amp;gt; lds, Job job) throws IOException;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;int estimateNumberOfReducers(Job job, MapReduceOper mapReduceOper) throws IOException;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This interface is evolving and hasn&apos;t yet been released so this is safe.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
