                            <comment id="13433323" author="dvryaboy" created="Mon, 13 Aug 2012 18:14:54 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Overall, I approve, but given the MRO, do we still need to pass in POLoads? They are trivially accessible from the MRO, and passing them in separately seems like an opportunity to pass in something wrong (an mro that doesn&apos;t actually have inputs from the supplied loaders).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
